    "It is possible that more nuanced or detailed scenarios would lead to different results.",
    "It is also possible that longer interactions would make the differences between humans and GPT more salient which would also lead to humans overperforming.",
    "Second, our findings suggest inherent differences between humans and GPT-4 in terms of complexity and the use of unique words.",
    "It's possible that merely using more complex or professional language is what drives the difference in quality, although our analysis did not provide evidence for this claim.",
